We compare against strong inference-time scaling paradigms in RAG:
(i) sequential refinement methods IRCoT trivedi2023ircot ,
Iter-RetGen shao2023iterretgen , and
DeepNote wang2025deepnote ;
(ii) sequential self-reflective correction method Self-RAG asai2024selfrag ;
and (iii) parallel drafting--verification method Speculative-RAG wang2024speculativerag .
